@startuml seq-model-deploy
title Развёртывание модели (Event-Driven FSM) — Enterprise ML Platform (Baseline/Alpha)

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 5

actor "ML Engineer" as MLE
participant "API Gateway\n(Kong/Envoy)" as GW
participant "Model Service\n(FastAPI)" as Model
participant "PostgreSQL" as PG
participant "Kafka\n(deploy-events)" as Kafka
participant "Deployment Service\n(Go/Temporal)" as Deploy
participant "Kubernetes API" as K8s
participant "Inference Service\n(Triton)" as Inf

== Загрузка артефакта (FSM: → Draft) ==

MLE -> GW : POST /v1/models\n{name, framework, artifact_url}
GW -> Model : REST forward (аутентификация пройдена)
Model -> PG : INSERT models (state=DRAFT,\ntenant_id, name, framework)\nidempotency_key
PG --> Model : model_id
Model --> GW : 201 Created {model_id, state: DRAFT}
GW --> MLE : 201 Created {model_id}

== Запрос развёртывания (FSM: Draft → Validating) ==

MLE -> GW : POST /v1/models/{id}/deploy
GW -> Model : REST forward
Model -> PG : UPDATE state=VALIDATING WHERE id=? AND state=DRAFT\n(оптимистичная блокировка)
PG --> Model : OK
Model -> Kafka : produce DeploymentRequested\n{model_id, tenant_id, version, artifact_url}
note right of Kafka
  Topic: deploy-events
  Kafka гарантирует at-least-once delivery.
  Deployment Service идемпотентен по model_id+version.
end note
Model --> GW : 202 Accepted {model_id, state: VALIDATING}
GW --> MLE : 202 Accepted\n(опросите GET /v1/models/{id} для статуса)

== Конвейер развёртывания (async event-driven) ==

Kafka -> Deploy : consume DeploymentRequested\n(CG: deployment-service)

note right of Deploy
  FSM: VALIDATING → STAGING → PRODUCTION
  Temporal Workflow гарантирует:
  - exactly-once переходы состояний
  - повтор при transient failures
  - явный откат при persistent failure
end note

Deploy -> Deploy : Валидация артефакта\n(схема входа/выхода, smoke test, FR-302)

alt Валидация провалена
    Deploy -> PG : UPDATE state=DRAFT, failure_reason=...
    Deploy -> Kafka : produce DeploymentFailed {model_id, reason}
    note right of Deploy : MLE получит уведомление\nчерез алертинг / polling
else Валидация пройдена (FSM: Validating → Staging)
    Deploy -> PG : UPDATE state=STAGING
    Deploy -> K8s : POST /apis/apps/v1/namespaces/ml-platform/deployments\n{image, model_id, resources, replicas}
    K8s --> Deploy : Deployment created

    == Health Check Loop (FSM: Staging → Production) ==

    loop Health checks (max 10 мин, FR-303)
        Deploy -> K8s : GET /api/v1/namespaces/ml-platform/pods?labelSelector=model_id=...
        K8s --> Deploy : Pod status (Running / Pending / CrashLoopBackOff)

        Deploy -> Inf : gRPC HealthCheck.Check(model_id)\n(smoke inference с тестовыми данными)

        alt Pod CrashLoopBackOff или smoke test failed
            note right of Deploy
              Автооткат: FSM STAGING → DRAFT.
              K8s Deployment масштабируется до 0.
              Предыдущая версия остаётся на 100% трафика.
            end note
            Deploy -> K8s : PATCH deployment replicas=0 (rollback)
            Deploy -> PG : UPDATE state=DRAFT, failure_reason=...
            Deploy -> Kafka : produce DeploymentRolledBack {model_id, reason}
        else Health check passed
            Deploy -> PG : UPDATE state=PRODUCTION
            Deploy -> Kafka : produce DeploymentSucceeded\n{model_id, endpoint, version}
            Deploy -> K8s : PATCH service traffic_weight=100% (canary complete)
            note right of Deploy : FSM: STAGING → PRODUCTION\nМодель обслуживает 100% трафика
        end
    end
end

MLE -> GW : GET /v1/models/{id}\n(polling статуса)
GW -> Model : REST forward
Model -> PG : SELECT state, deployment_url WHERE id=?
PG --> Model : {state: PRODUCTION, endpoint: ...}
Model --> GW : 200 OK {state: PRODUCTION}
GW --> MLE : 200 OK {model_id, state, endpoint}

@enduml